2. **Recall**: This criterion checks if all target objects are localized by a bounding box. Since there are no bounding boxes present in the image, none of the crawler cranes are localized.

3. **Fit**: This criterion checks if each bounding box is neither too loose nor too tight. Again, without any bounding boxes present, I cannot evaluate the fit.
